    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊银行可能因支付费用削减而遭受 1 亿欧元损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/greek-banks-may-face-a-100-million-hit-from-cut-to-payment-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲银行股票投资公司 SA 称，希腊银行因减少或取消银行向客户收取的各种支付费用可能面临约 1 亿欧元（1.05 亿美元）的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/greek-banks-may-face-a-100-million-hit-from-cut-to-payment-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 08:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
